{"tid":2257251,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"支那又輸！美國技術大突破！鈣鈦礦太陽能電池，光電轉換效率為矽晶兩倍！","createTime":"2020-10-25T04:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T12:01:53.000Z","uid":32511,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"4c11c0db278d811d02ade7573fcb1bbb902d2c0c","tid":2257251,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T04:07:41.000Z","msg":"光電技術出現重大突破！目前市面上的太陽能電池能源轉換效率差，只能把極少量的光能轉為電力。不過美國能源部所屬的橡樹嶺國家實驗室（Oak Ridge National Laboratory）研發出鈣鈦礦（perovskite）太陽能電池，能源轉換效率高達 66%，是主流太陽能電池的兩倍以上。<br />\n<br />\nOilPrice、CleanTechnica 報導，目前光電技術以矽晶太陽能為主，此種太陽能電池堅固耐用，成本也不斷下降，但是一大缺點是能源轉換效率極差。最平價的矽晶太陽能電池，受到方位、傾斜角度、天候影響，能源轉換效率只有 7~16%。理論上來說，矽晶太陽能的能源轉換效率最高可達 30%，但是實際上商用面板的轉換效率很少達到 25%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2020/10/22/oak-perovskite-solar-battery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2020%2F10%2F22%2Foak-perovskite-solar-battery%2F&d=FHegwWfkEdb3mv0CWz72PQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=cb5cdf0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2020/10/22/oak-perovskite-solar-battery/</a>"},{"pid":"7a18fb176ea7390f5c0007d5d1131a7dadafc976","tid":2257251,"uid":48083,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T04:09:19.000Z","msg":"係既話就支國成個太陽能板行業收皮<br />\n千祈唔好俾人偷技術"},{"pid":"7c7856c2339d799a9debe5980de9e2345cd3d514","tid":2257251,"uid":191926,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T04:10:16.000Z","msg":"中國:Thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;(抄來用)"},{"pid":"82d3d341856d284b117151b15646bb0d71cef4ac","tid":2257251,"uid":54373,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T04:11:13.000Z","msg":"我哋藍絲又輸了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35180894011370a885420a4c16d1a04e066eb0f5","tid":2257251,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T04:15:09.000Z","msg":"都玩人造太陽啦 無限既潔淨能源"},{"pid":"44dab4bb748baef49e271a785c8911bdb780b536","t